    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "resilience feels like such a hollow word though. like, what's the point of being resilient for a future that's just gonna be a series of disasters? it feels more like we're just being told to stay on a sinking ship because it's \"brave\" to drown. it honestly feels more logical to just not be part of it all. why suffer through the decline if it's all inevitable anyway?",
